<L>__{interior second car. day.}
<A>__{at the top of the laugh, cut to the interior of the second car, riding right in back of them. the atmosphere is completely unlike the cozy and jolly scene preceding. we have dead silence. bonnie is driving, smoking a cigarette, grim. blanche seated as far away as she can get from bonnie without falling out of the car makes a face at the cigarette smoke, rolls down the window for air. c.w.'s in the back seat, just staring.}
